---
const ctaBenefits = [
  "Mulai gratis tanpa proses yang rumit",
  "Pantau keuangan lebih rapi setiap hari",
  "Akses nyaman di mobile maupun web",
];
---

<section
  class="bg-[#fff] px-7 py-16 md:px-20 md:py-24"
  aria-labelledby="cta-title"
>
  <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-400">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl text-center">
      <h2
        id="cta-title"
        class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-[-0.04em] text-slate-950 md:text-6xl"
      >
        Siap Mengambil Kendali atas Keuangan Anda?
      </h2>

      <p
        class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-4xl text-sm font-medium leading-relaxed text-slate-600 md:text-2xl"
      >
        Bergabung bersama banyak pengguna yang mulai mengatur pemasukan,
        pengeluaran, dan target anggaran dengan lebih tenang lewat
        ExpenseTracker.
      </p>

      <ul
        class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-5 gap-y-3 text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 md:text-lg"
        aria-label="Keunggulan utama ExpenseTracker"
      >
        {
          ctaBenefits.map((benefit) => (
            <li class="inline-flex items-center gap-2">
              <span
                class="inline-block h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500"
                aria-hidden="true"
              />
              <span>{benefit}</span>
            </li>
          ))
        }
      </ul>

      <div
        class="mt-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:gap-5"
      >
        <a
          href="/register"
          class="inline-flex min-h-[56px] w-full items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-emerald-500 px-8 py-4 text-base font-bold text-white transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-emerald-600 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-emerald-500 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 sm:w-auto sm:min-w-[240px] md:min-h-[64px] md:text-2xl"
          aria-label="Mulai gratis dengan ExpenseTracker"
        >
          Mulai Gratis
        </a>

        <a
          href="/login"
          class="inline-flex min-h-[56px] w-full items-center justify-center rounded-2xl border-2 border-emerald-500 bg-transparent px-8 py-4 text-base font-bold text-emerald-500 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-emerald-50 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-emerald-500 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 sm:w-auto sm:min-w-[240px] md:min-h-[64px] md:text-2xl"
          aria-label="Masuk ke akun ExpenseTracker"
        >
          Masuk ke Akun
        </a>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-6 text-xs font-medium text-slate-400 md:text-base">
        Cocok untuk kebutuhan harian, perencanaan bulanan, dan kebiasaan
        finansial yang lebih sehat.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
